The epic conclusion to the year of staching and bashing. Vote for your favorite stache betweeen myself, @sagenewman, @tannerbutner, or @kolbywanchuk. Every dollar is a vote, with 100% of the proceeds going to an amazing organization: The Golden Circle of Champions.

#Repost @broncridingnation with @use.repost
・・・
SWIPE THROUGH, THEN USE THIS QR CODE TO VOTE FOR WHO WORE IT BEST! All proceeds to Golden Circle of Champions, Santa Maria Elks support program for kids battling cancer. HERE’s the story —

A year ago, Chase Brooks, Tanner Butner, Sage Newman & Kolby Wanchuk decided to grow mustaches and who of the Mustache Krewe shaved first owed the others a day’s recreation the next time they had a day. Nobody shaved. SO — new deal. 

Every $1 is a vote — vote online as many times as you want. PLEASE repost.

The winner gets to tell the other three what they have to do with their mustaches.

If you’re at NFR, you can vote with cash at the Golden Circle event on Sunday or DAILY at Skiver Boots Showroom at Renaissance Hotel (3400 Paradise.
